>> Home Component <<
1) Home component consist of two sub components:
   i) Search 
   ii) QuickSearch
2) It is act as a container for Search and QuickSearch components
3) Home component layout is divided into 2 different components i.e. Search
   and QuickSearch 


>> Search Component <<
1) Search folder is the upper part of our Home component 
2) It consist of background-image, title text, search city and restaurants
   dropdown options


>> QuickSearch Component <<
1) QuickSearch is the lower part of our Home component
2) QuickSearch contains text and a sub component i.e. QuickDisplay 


>> QuickDisplay << 
1) QuickDisplay is child of QuickSearch component
2) QuickDisplay consist of meal type cards 



